<div class='commit-subject'>vrend: never destroy context 0 in vrend_renderer_context_destroy</div><div class='commit-msg'>There will be a crash if the guest destroy context 0. As the context 0 is
allocate in renderer init, not destroy in vrend_renderer_context_destroy.
The context will be freed in renderer fini by calling vrend_decode_reset.

Signed-off-by: Li Qiang &lt;liq3ea@gmail.com&gt;
Signed-off-by: Dave Airlie &lt;airlied@redhat.com&gt;
